WEBVTT

00:00:25.831 --> 00:00:30.001
"Minha vida tinha sido
uma arma carregada", diz o verso,

00:00:30.001 --> 00:00:31.611
e eu o escrevo no quadro,

00:00:31.611 --> 00:00:35.041
fazendo pausas para que eles
possam gritar os antônimos.

00:00:35.041 --> 00:00:36.245
"Meu."

00:00:36.245 --> 00:00:37.525
"Seu."

00:00:37.525 --> 00:00:38.815
"Vida."

00:00:38.815 --> 00:00:40.045
"Morte."

00:00:40.045 --> 00:00:42.065
"Havia ficado em pé?"

00:00:42.065 --> 00:00:43.945
"Sentará"

00:00:43.945 --> 00:00:44.945
"Um."

00:00:44.945 --> 00:00:45.945
"Muitos."

00:00:45.945 --> 00:00:46.965
"Carregada."

00:00:46.965 --> 00:00:48.155
"Vazia."

00:00:48.155 --> 00:00:49.375
"Arma?"

00:00:50.615 --> 00:00:51.615
"Arma."

00:00:51.615 --> 00:00:52.615
(Disparo)

00:00:52.615 --> 00:00:53.859
Por um momento,

00:00:53.859 --> 00:00:57.189
muito parecido com o que está
entre o raio e o som dele,

00:00:57.189 --> 00:00:59.399
as crianças só olham para mim,

00:00:59.399 --> 00:01:00.689
e então chega: